text: Backlog, ocena przepisana z untappd, w ramach uzupełniania profilu na ratebeer. CBC #170 CHORE. Barwa z kosmosu, genialna owocowość i kwasowość, ZERO śladów alkoholu. Nawet nie wiem jak to skomentować.

Sample @ CBC Boston, 2016. Thick, vividly electric purple pour with a massive light purple head that eventually settles. Smells and drinks like a blueberry milkshake. Sweet and just a bit tart. Extremely juicy. Some earthy, acidic fruit skin. Full bodied, approaching thick. Interesting stuff that sort of drives the idea of a fruit beer to the extreme. Fun to try.
Looks like blueberry milkshake. this is not beer, its still awesome though. I cant describe it other than it is just blueberry and nothing else.

Draught at All in Beer Fest 2016 session 3, 2016-11-05 Göteborg AR:tart, blueberries, dryness AP: blueberry blue colored body, wee purple head F: tart, dry, blueberries - this was the surprise beer at Session 2 - but didnt show up until session 3 = no que ;) 3,7

Draught @ CBC 2016 [ Green Session ]. - Copenhagen Beer Celebration 2016, Oksnehallen Vesterbro, Halmtorvet 11, 1700 Copenhagen, Denmark. [ As Mikkeller SpontanQuadrupelBlueberry ].Clear dark brown - purple color with a large, frothy, good lacing, fully lasting, purple head. Aroma is moderate blueberry, tart, sweet blueberry - berries, butterscotch. Flavor is moderate sweet and light acidic with a average duration, tart, blueberry, sweet blueberry, dry. Body is medium, texture is oily to watery, carbonation is soft. [20160514]
 7-4-8-3-15
Sample at All In Beer Fest 2016. Thick hazy purple with pink head. A lot of blueberries and sour fruit. Really nice quite high ABV blueberry soup!

Fat på All In Beer Fest, Göteborg. Hann tyvärr bara få den sista slatten innan fatet tog slut. Mörkt blåröd, grumlig med högt, härligt rosa skum. Både ser ut som och smakar som blåbärssoppa. Den stora syrligheten balanseras upp bra med sötma. Ruskigt bärig och frisk. Snygg för ögat och i munnen.

All In Beerfest 2016: Dat color!! Aroma is fruity and tart with obvious blueberries and citrus sourness. Taste is tart and sour blueberries, lactic notes, lemonjuice and light black currant(?). Nice berry-bomb.

Draft sampled at CBC Boston 2016 with Andrew and Brendan. Pours a deep pink purple body with spotty pink lacing. Nose is strong, assertive fruit seeds (wouldve pinned it to be raspberry). Mouthfeel is medium and ultra tart. One note raspberry/blueberry tartness, but its great.
Draft at CBC - pours purple - nose/taste of blueberry on blueberry on blueberry on blueberry, funky jam and oak - medium body

Sample on draft at fofa. Opaque black purple pour with dense, deep purple foam. Aroma is quite pungent, tons of blueberry, very jammy, not much funk tbh, basically just concentrated blueberry juice. Taste is quite tart, citric blueberry flavor, light puckering. Palate is med bodied with good carbonation. Tasty.
Draft. A black beer with a pinkish head. The aroma has notes of blueberries, and malt. The flavor is acidic and dominated by blueberries, leading to a tart finish.

Tap at FoFA. Ultra deep purple with a thick medium sized dark pinkish-purple head, good retention, leaving some lacing and blueberry legs on the glass. Aroma is intensely blueberry forward with strong winey notes (probably just because of the blueberries), some funk hidden behind the fruits and mild lemony presence. Taste is of blueberries pureee / smoothie with moderate acidity, a blueberry dessert wine sweetness and thickness impression and lemony notes. Medium body but super thick mouthfeel. Moderate carbonation. Vinous. Strong and sticky blueberry finish. Its so thick and intense that it gets cloying rather quickly but the fruity presence is great and authentic. It feels like a nicely funked up blueberry smoothie.
At Hills farmsteads FoFa. Awesomely deep purple, like frikin beet juice with a pink head. Tons of waxy blueberry aroma and flavor. Great.

Tap @ CBC 16. Pours insane purple with a pink head. Aroma of blueberry smoothie, lactic tartness, berry pie and blueberry juicy. The taste is tart and slight lactic with tons of blueberry notes in different shapes. Just extremely refreshing and over the top in a way that I really like. Where is the alcohol - pretty please..

CBC 2016 Green session. Purple body with a big pink head. Aroma of blueberries, tart fruit, leather. Taste is strong blueberry, sour and lactic, funky towards the finish, but this beer is dominated by the berries. Quite nice, and probably healthy.
Draught at CBC #5. Pitch purple/black - pink head. Blueberry juice. High high blueberry. Sweet. Tart. Zesty. Peppery. Flowery. Ok acidic. Power..... almost only blueberry juice !

Aroma and taste is bold, intense, rich in your face blueberry, medium sour, berry skin, stone fruit, medium acidic, resonating intense blueberry finish. Wonderful.
From tap at CBC 2016. Dark reddish colour with a pink head. Aroma and flavour of blueberries, tartness, barnyard and acidic.
Keg at cbc16.. Deep red purple... Thin red lacing.. Soft sweet barnyard funk nose.. Heavy fruit.. Soft blueberries big funk

Draught @ CBC 2016. Pours black with a huge dense pink/red head, easily the best looking beer of the festival. Aroma of light sourness, rich tart fruity, rich blueberries, lemon notes. Flavor is sour, light sweet, intense fruity, berries, rich blueberry, citrus, lemon. Medium to full body, soft carbonation, acidic finish with a bit of alcohol warmth. 140516
CBC. Almost black with purple/red head. Aroma is blueberries, sour and fruit. Flavour is malt, blueberries, sour, lemon, wood and tart.
Tap @ Copenhagen Beer Celebration, 2016. Dark red body with a medium dark pink head. Blueberries, yoghurt, zesty, tart.

From tap at Copenhagen Beer Celebration 2016 - Green session. Very dark purple color, almost black with red notes and pink-purple head. Aroma is Tart fruity, blueberries, barnyard notes, lactic acid notes. Light sweet and heavy acidic fruity taste. Medium oily body with soft carbonation.

Draught @ CBC 2016, Green session, København
Pours black with a deep purple head. Aroma has notes of malt, tart, blueberry funk and berry. Taste is medium sweet and medium sour with a long dry, tart, funky and blueberry finish. Body is medium, texture is thin to oily, carbonation is soft.
From tap. Pours dark purple and with a purple head. Aroma is dense blueberry. Thick blueberry, dense, shivering sourish. Lingering fruity, intense blueberry. Juicy and rather dry.
CBC. Black with a big and lasting purple head. Aroma is sweet, malty, heavy blueberries, and barnyard. Flavor is quite sweet and rather acidic. Dry and rather acidic finish. 140516
Tap @ Copenhagen Beer Celebration, 2016. Pours deep amber with a purple head. Yoghurt - massive, berries, lacto. Quite off. Soothing youghurt. Impressed with ths other ratings!
Sample @ CBC16, Copenhagen. Green session. Opaque purple pour with a pinkish head. Tastes of blueberry soup, has some light funk and a pleasant tartness. Im a sucker for these beers :)

[5/14/16] Draught sample at Copenhagen Beer Celebration 2016. Green session. Amazing deep purple with lighter purple head. Great blueberries aroma with some funk. Wonderful juicy blueberries flavor, tart and funky. Rounded mouthfeel. Amazing.
tap cbc. Pours cloudy purple with a purple head. Aroma huge blueberry, berries, fruits, loads of yogurt, light spicey. Taste is heavy berrys, tart, yogurt. Quite flithy.
Sample at CBC 2016. Fruity smell with blueberries. Lots of blueberries in the taste. Tart and funky. Long aftertaste. Dry finish.

Sample at CBC 2016. 

Dark purple with a nice purple head. Tart with blueberries, grapes, some citrus and caramel. The body was medium as was the carbonation. Long finish.
CBC 2016. Pours a very intense red with a large frothy red head. Aromas of blueberry. Period. Taste is blueberry. Period. Mouthfeel is tart and very dry with medium carbonation.

On tap at CBC 16 Green Session. Pours an opaque black / purple with a nice dark pink head. Tart with a mellow bitterness. Shitloads of blueberry aromas with hints of almonds and metals. Full bodied. High carbonation. Long bitter finish with lots more blueberries.

#3600... Yay...? Worthy beer for that honour though. Pours deep purple burgundy with deep purple head. Aroma of blueberries, bretta, light liquored cherries. Taste is blueberries, mellow to rich tart. Body is light to medium, smooth with soft carbonation.

Green session, Copenhagen Beer Celebration 2016. Dark purple beer with a nice and lasting purple head. Fruity blueberry aroma, citrus, grapes, caramel, some astringent nots. Sourish blueberry flavor, tart, astringent, floral notes, some wild strawberries. Quite nice

14.05.2016, tap @ CBC:
Nice deep purple creamy longlasting head, deep deep purple color. Aroma is dry concentrated fruity, masses of blueberries, berry skin, oak, grass, heather, sorrel. Taste is dry concentrated fruity, masses of dry sour blueberries, berry skin, heather, grass, sorrel, oak, fruit stones. Medium bitterness, dry sour-ish mouthfeel. Very nice.
CBC. Deep, dark red with a thick purple pink head. Aroma of yoghurt, red berries and spice. Dry and very tart flavour with intense sour berries and a hint of funk
Tap @CBC16. Deep red, almost black with red, thick and frothy head. Insane! Sourish blueberry aroma. Flavour is big and fat blueberry, sour and sticky, Great.

Tap @CBC 2016.
Intensive red aroma, pink head.
The aroma consists mostly of blueberry of course, but also some barnyard notes. Blueberry mostly in flavor. Like drinking slightly too tart blueberry juice.
@Copenhagen Beer Celebration 2016, GREENdark red. Intense dark berries, barny rich nose. Good bodied, tart. Long finish. Pretty nice.-- rated with beerbasher/winphone

duft: sur rød bær duft: 
smag: syr tør bær duft blåbær. intens tør sur røde bær
CBC2016. Fast schwarze Farbe, sehr schöne pinke Schaumkrone. Geruch intensiv fruchtig, rote Früchte, säuerlich. Geschmack pelzig, säuerlich, rote Früchte holzig, Äpfel.

Pours blueberry with large purple head
Aromas tart of blueberries, blueberries, and blueberries, and some funky cracked garden branches
Taste has tart notes of blueberries, hints of black currant and cracked garden branch
